## PAYMENT

## success
## Правило №1

-------------------- rule

POST /payment

~ headers
example: ranges_payment_with_reversal

~ body
jpath: $.amount >> {{ range: payment.amount/success }}

----- response

~ body
{
    ## reversal по этому id вернет success
    "id": {{ range: payment.id/default }}, 
    "status": "success"
}


